snippet.title: REACTION/THOUGHTS Amber Heard as Mera (ON-SET AQUAMAN PHOTOS)
snippet.description:
futurefilmmaker39480 gives his official reaction and thoughts on the on-set photos of the upcoming sixth DCEU entry, "Aquaman", with Amber Heard as Queen Mera.  Tell him your thoughts on the photos down below?  Are you excited or not excited to see her as Mera? Do you think that the costume looks great? Do you think she looks great in the costume?

And you'll have to forgive me when I did this video in voiceover, I used my regular sound record on my laptop.

DISCLAIMER: I do not own any of the music or photos that are used within this video.   Aquaman is owned by Warner Bros. Pictures, DC Entertainment and Ratpac-Dune Entertainment.
